title: Eco-Dome Al'Dani mapping changes/auto-route improvements and minor bugfixes

changes.change: Harrier's Call and the latest drums are now properly recognized as Bloodlust spells.

Eco-Dome Al'Dani performance has been drastically improved. This also caused a shift in the mapping to much better reflect where the enemies are in-game whch has been submitted for change to MDT as well.
